---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Poland of Our Dreams — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Poland of Our Dreams</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Warsaw | 2019</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Explores dreams, desires, and aspirations for Poland's future. What does the Leader dream of? The exhibition investigates contemporary uncertainties and asks whether naïve dreams of a colorful, socially emancipated, prude-free society are inherently political.</p>
      <p>A key work is "Dreamer" by Marcin Kaliński, featuring a photograph of Poland's political leader with eyes closed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Marceli Adamczyk, Øleg&Kaśka, Małgorzata Goliszewska, Marcin Kaliński, Iza Koczanowska, Aleksandra Liput, Grzegorz Łoznikow, Anna Raczyńska, Michał Sosiński</p>
      <p><strong>Curators:</strong> Dzidy (Michalina Sablik, Aleksandra Liput)</p>
      <p><strong>Photographer:</strong> Bartosz Górka</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/poland-of-our-dreams/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
